<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>617</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>zhǔ mìng dìng wǒ men de lù 迦南617</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ mìng dìng wǒ men de lù jiǎo dòng wǒ men de cháo wō
 cóng cǐ wǒ men jiù lí kāi jiā zài fēng yǔ zhōng chuān suō
 jǐn guǎn lǚ tú jiān xīn jǐn guǎn yù dào lěng mò
 yī xiǎng dào shén wú bǐ de dà ài jiù shén me yě bù shuō
 méi yǒu bào dá yǎng yù zhī ēn zhī dào nǐ xīn lǐ hěn nán guò
 fàng xīn ba bǎ qīn rén jiāo gěi zhǔ zhǔ bì huì wèi nǐ zuò
 xiāng hù gěi yī gè ān wèi xiōng zhōng dōu yǒu yī tuán ài huǒ
 zhè gè shí dài wǒ men bù jì mò bù shì zhǐ yǒu nǐ yī gè.</lyrics>
</song>